line_1: Did I take delight to fetter
line_2: Thrice ten thousand times your betters

line_1: Tho' Rhyme serves the Thoughts of great Poets to fetter,
line_2: It sets off the Sense of small Poets the better.

line_1: And lead haughty kings in his fetter.
line_2: As your topic than these is much better,

line_1: My mind without a single fetter;
line_2: My health was good, my spirits better,
